# PyInstaller
#  Usually these files are written by a single script from a single folder.
#  So, along with CWD, we ignore --workpath, --specpath and --distpath
#  In most cases, --workpath is CWD, and --specpath is CWD.
#  --distpath is CWD/dist on Windows and CWD/dist on other platforms.
*.spec
dist/

